{"tid":934994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這家麵攤老闆娘低胸爆乳煮麵 網友揪團：吃麵了！","createTime":"2018-12-09T16:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T18:08:53.000Z","uid":212399,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1a28855461f1ba598f7e3d8c21d356fb3b28cf65","tid":934994,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T16:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/09/99/5639849.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F09%2F99%2F5639849.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=78ac1494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國曼谷一間麵攤的老闆娘，因為穿著清涼，身材火辣，吸引許多男客人上門光顧。&nbsp;<br />\n現在享受美食都要講究「色香味」俱全，在泰國曼谷有家麵攤的老闆娘近日成為網路紅人，原因是因為她身材火辣，煮麵時穿著低胸上衣，「北半球」呼之欲出，消息一出，也吸引許多「醉翁之意不在酒」的客人上門想一窺究竟。<br />\n據《khaosod》報導，這家位在曼谷的麵攤，老闆娘有著一頭烏黑長髮，長相清秀亮麗，煮麵時穿著低胸小可愛和短褲，露出小蠻腰和深邃的雙峰「事業線」，有時還會穿著露背小洋裝，火辣的身材讓男客人快噴鼻血。<br />\n雖然外表受到關注，但是她煮麵、切小菜的動作一點也不馬虎，即使有人在拍，老闆娘也大方的給予甜美的笑容，讓網友看了快融化。有網友看了稱讚「出名了」、「準備訂機票了」、「廣聚人心的麵店」、「麵好不好吃已經不重要了」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3527175?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F3527175%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=9weJ2qoQPFEbcYmxTI9AOsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8194b511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3527175?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"33744540b1e29cf694eb57f09f1fee149a0a465c","tid":934994,"uid":3549,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"有鳩不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/pic.ctitv.com/wpimg/2018/08/07163816/FotoJet-53